Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Babe, babe, babe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bubee, bubee
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.10,0:01:20.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe, babe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.07,0:01:26.74,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Ooh, ooh, ooh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.74,0:01:28.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Você é meu pequeno companheiro
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.78,0:01:33.33,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Ei, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.03,0:01:33.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Bubee, bubee, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Meu coração está acelerado
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.66,0:01:39.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}O que se reflete nesses olhos
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.29,0:01:42.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}São as cores de um novo mundo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Woah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.63,0:01:47.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Fique ao meu lado hoje também
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.26,0:01:50.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vamos seguir enquanto seguro sua mão
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.26,0:01:54.05,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Anseio por um lugar onde eu possa brilhar
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.64,0:02:00.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Enquanto um som mágico ecoa
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Eu quero cantar com você
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vamos cantar juntos
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.57,0:02:09.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Você é uma estrela que brilha intensamente
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Meu bubee, bubee, bubee love
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Podemos ser estrelas brilhantes
