Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:56.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Que parecia que sempre ficaria ao meu lado){当たり前に隣にいた}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}a procurar por você{君を探してる}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:02.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Vou enquadrar uma foto de nós dois e pendurar{二人映るフレームデコレート}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Vou organizar tudo do meu jeito, como eu quiser, como realmente é{思うがままわがままありのままに並べよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:10.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Nossa sintonia: somar, subtrair, multiplicar, dividir por...{相性プラスマイナスマルチプライディバイドバイ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:10.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Eu amo tudo isso!{全部好き}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Me chamando, te chamando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:15.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(E Você)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Quero subir as escadas do futuro com você{君と歩きたい未来ステアーズ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&\i1}Lucky lucky shiny{\i0}, nossos corações vibrando em sonhos{Lucky lucky shiny, 二人のトキメキドリーミング}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Se amanhã o céu estiver limpo, vai ficar tudo bem{明日晴れなら何時もオーライ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Talvez eu esteja um pouco triste e fraco {ちょっとブルー ウィークネス}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:29.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Mas Feliz!){(But happy!)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Mas quando estou com você, me sinto salva{けど君がいるからfeel safe}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Não existe tempo perdido{無駄な時間なんてない}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Vamos esperar a chuva passar{雨上がる空をwait until}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:39.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Olha para o céu! Se fizer isso{You look 見上げたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Coragem está em dois mundos, juntos agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:43.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Essa é a prova!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}É isso que nos conecta{それが２つ結ぶ絆だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:49.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Todos sorriem para garotas bonitas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:52.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{=12}{\fad(150,150)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord4\blur5\3c&HFFFFFF&}Que tipo de futuro essa holofote irá iluminar?{どんな明日を照らすのかspotlight}
